SUMMARY:BoHoss Boogie at Rio Nido Roadhouse
DESCRIPTION:Shake off the week with live music from BoHoss Boogie — a Sonoma County favorite bringing their signature blend of blues\, rock\, and boogie to the stage. Known for gritty guitar riffs\, soulful vocals\, and danceable grooves\, this local crew has built a loyal following across the North Bay with high-energy sets that keep the crowd moving. \nCome unwind\, grab a drink\, and let BoHoss Boogie do the rest. \n 
