SUMMARY:Peacetown continues at HopMonk with Frank & The Bone Machine
DESCRIPTION:Frank & The Bone Machine is a band of internationally renowned touring and recording musicians that perform a rebrand\, melancholic\, and punk jazz set of Tom Waits songs. \nWhether or not the songs of Tom Waits play a central role in your music collection\, you have to experience this show live to feel the heaven-opening maelstrom of beauty scarcely captured by a live band. From Martha to Downtown Train\, Bone Machine brings the heart\, atmosphere\, and sweat to performances brimming with a ramshackle sophistication and honesty as well as the renowned Waitsian monologues full of the funny anecdotes for which Mr. Waits is universally celebrated. \nFrom bourbon-soaked ballads to evocative Godliness and anarchic elegance\, there has never been a show that has captured the golden thread of what makes Waits such a legend until now!
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/peacetown-continues-at-hopmonk-with-frank-the-bone-machine/
LOCATION:HopMonk Tavern – Sebastopol\, 230 Petaluma Ave\, Sebastopol\, CA
CATEGORIES:Music
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://golocal.coop/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Bone-machine-band-s.jpg
GEO:38.4012;-122.823
