SUMMARY:Benefit for Project Hope for Palestine
DESCRIPTION:Featuring Dan Martin\nAll proceeds go to Project Hope for Palestine\n\nBenefit for Project Hope for Palestine – A Night of Music & Poetry \nJoin us at Starling Bar for a special benefit event featuring Dan Martin and an evening of music\, poetry\, and community in support of Project Hope for Palestine\, a Palestinian-founded and led mutual aid project working in Gaza. \nAll proceeds from the evening will go directly toward supporting their work. The event will also feature remarks from Project Hope founder Iyas Sartawi.
