SUMMARY:Pee-Wee's Big Adventure Movie Night at Cloverdale Performing Arts Center
DESCRIPTION:The famous movie cult classic is coming to Cloverdale Performing Arts Center. \nThe love of Pee-wee Herman’s life is his bicycle. When it is stolen\, he is send on a wild cross country adventure after a fortune teller tells him his bicycle is in the basement of the Alamo. Along the way\, Pee-wee encounters an escaped convict\, a waitress with wanderlust and a jealous boyfriend\, and a mysterious female truck driver.
